org.apache.hadoop.hbase.regionserver

Class CSLMImmutableSegment

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.regionserver.Segment
      • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.regionserver.ImmutableSegment
        • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.regionserver.CSLMImmutableSegment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MemStoreSizing

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
public class CSLMImmutableSegment
extends ImmutableSegment
    CSLMImmutableSegment is an abstract class that extends the API supported by a Segment, and ImmutableSegment. This immutable segment is working with CellSet with ConcurrentSkipListMap (CSLM) delegatee.
